            "recommendation": "Remove WellnessBankDebugActivity from the production release build. Set android:exported=false in the release manifest or remove the Activity declaration. Add a BuildConfig.DEBUG runtime guard in onCreate that finishes the Activity when BuildConfig.DEBUG == false. Implement Play Integrity API attestation at app startup. Reference: android:exported=false, BuildConfig.DEBUG guard, com.google.android.play:integrity.",
            "effort-estimate": "Medium"
          }
